# 3.1.1.research.internal.q9.keyrack-glob-support

## question

does keyrack unlock support glob patterns like `--key 'CLAUDE_OAUTH_TOKEN_*'`?

## options

- yes, glob works today
- no, need to implement
- partial (some commands support, others don't)

## why it matters

glob support enables clean UX: `rhx keyrack unlock --key 'TOKEN_*'` instead of N separate commands.

## research approach

check keyrack source code, test with glob pattern, verify behavior.

## note

this is internal research — check rhachet codebase.

